description:
Danny welcomes Drew Sidora from The Real Housewives of Atlanta to talk about what's to come this season, her relationship with the other women, her acting work in Step Up, The Game, and so much more! After that, Danny chats with RuPaul's Drag Race All Stars 3 WINNER Trixie Mattel about Real Housewives, career, new music, and lots more!


Drew Sidora Interview: 2:38ish

Trixie Mattel Interview: 37:48ish
